# Link base URLs (Jira, Git, TC, DMS) are runtime-config via Spring backend —
# set PORTAL_LINKS_JIRA_BASE_URL / PORTAL_LINKS_GIT_BASE_URL /
# PORTAL_LINKS_TC_BASE_URL / PORTAL_LINKS_DMS_BASE_URL as env vars on the
# Spring process; they are served to the SPA via GET /portal/info at runtime.
# No Vite build-time variables are needed for link configuration.
